# Checkbox Demo - different checkbox styles
Source demos/settings.tape
Output demos/gifs/checkbox.gif

Hide
Type "cargo run --example checkbox_demo"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Show

Sleep 800ms

# Toggle first checkbox
Space
Sleep 600ms

# Move to next and toggle
Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

# Continue through checkboxes
Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 600ms

# Go back and untoggle one
Shift+Tab
Sleep 400ms
Space
Sleep 800ms

Sleep 1s

Type "q"
